reviews.review_description:
Sooo glad they gave a demo to this game, I probably would not have downloaded otherwise based on screenshots. Retro feel with pixel art menus, the overworld is a fun concept and still get that 3d 2st person immersion through battling. Plus for a real rpg leveling system as well! Will definitely be purchasing the real game. 

I know it's still in development but can I request an online arena in the future?! Competition is my favorite part of games, even something simple would suffice. 

5* devs =}
